oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Parrott's Tourist Camp, Boom, Tennessee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Color photograph of buildings at Parrott's Tourist Camp near Lake Boom, Tennessee. A car is parked behind the main building in front. A sign hangs above the doorway and reads "Parrott Cafe / Tourist Cabins." Features a divided back and faded handwritten correspondence on reverse. [No. 35858]
